1
00:00:28,750 --> 00:00:30,333
[HARUHI laughing]

2
00:00:32,125 --> 00:00:33,083
[TANIGUCHI]
Huh?

3
00:00:38,625 --> 00:00:39,583
[KYON sighs]

4
00:00:40,708 --> 00:00:42,333
[HARUHI]
Well, here we are!

5
00:00:43,583 --> 00:00:46,250
[KYON] Doesn't that mean
we shouldn't be going in?

6
00:00:46,333 --> 00:00:50,166
Even little kids would avoid
shooting in a spot like this.

7
00:00:50,250 --> 00:00:52,000
Except for the stupid ones,
that is.

8
00:00:52,083 --> 00:00:53,500
[HARUHI]
Don't just stand there.

9
00:00:53,583 --> 00:00:55,500
Hurry up and climb over already!

10
00:00:55,583 --> 00:00:58,208
[KYON] Oops, forgot.
She's really stupid.

11
00:00:58,291 --> 00:00:59,875
Come on, Mikuru. Hurry up!

12
00:00:59,958 --> 00:01:00,916
[gasps]

13
00:01:02,708 --> 00:01:03,250
Mm-mm...

14
00:01:03,333 --> 00:01:04,166
[laughs]

15
00:01:04,250 --> 00:01:05,625
The fence is rather high;

16
00:01:05,708 --> 00:01:07,875
it might be too difficult
for everyone to climb over.

17
00:01:07,958 --> 00:01:10,708
Would you have
a solution for us?

18
00:01:10,791 --> 00:01:11,750
[KYON]
Hm?

19
00:01:14,375 --> 00:01:15,958
[gasps]

20
00:01:16,041 --> 00:01:18,583
Wow, that gate's
gotta be really old...

21
00:01:18,666 --> 00:01:22,083
[TANIGUCHI] Am I gonna have to
play a sea monster or somethin'?

22
00:01:22,166 --> 00:01:24,333
[TSURUYA] The lake didn't always
have this fence around it.

23
00:01:24,416 --> 00:01:26,375
You know, people used
to fall in a lot.

24
00:01:26,458 --> 00:01:28,875
[KYON] Thank god,
they're all so clueless.

25
00:01:36,375 --> 00:01:37,875
[HARUHI]
There. That'll do the trick.

26
00:01:37,958 --> 00:01:40,125
So this is the scene
where Mikuru gets cornered

27
00:01:40,208 --> 00:01:41,500
by the baddie.

28
00:01:41,583 --> 00:01:44,208
She can't use her beam
'cause Yuki neutralized it.

29
00:01:44,291 --> 00:01:46,458
Well, the cue cards are done.

30
00:01:46,541 --> 00:01:48,166
Here, hang onto this
for me, kid.

31
00:01:48,250 --> 00:01:49,208
Huh?!

32
00:01:49,291 --> 00:01:51,083
[HARUHI]
Mikuru, are you ready?

33
00:01:51,166 --> 00:01:53,333
[whimpers] Yes.

34
00:01:53,416 --> 00:01:54,375
[HARUHI]
Come on, louder!

35
00:01:54,458 --> 00:01:55,416
Yes!

36
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:56,833
[KYON]
I feel your pain.

37
00:01:56,916 --> 00:01:58,625
[HARUHI]
Okay! Here we go!

38
00:01:58,708 --> 00:02:01,166
And... action!

39
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:02,208
[yelps]

40
00:02:03,458 --> 00:02:05,083
[MIKURU]
E-E-Even in times like this,

41
00:02:05,166 --> 00:02:06,750
I won't ever run away!

42
00:02:06,833 --> 00:02:10,125
Y-You're an evil bad alien...

43
00:02:10,208 --> 00:02:13,708
And... now, you better
leave this planet at once!

44
00:02:13,791 --> 00:02:14,958
[HARUHI]
Cut!

45
00:02:15,041 --> 00:02:17,375
[NAGATO] For he is very
valuable to us, you see.

46
00:02:17,458 --> 00:02:19,708
And while we're seizing him
and his hidden powers,

47
00:02:19,791 --> 00:02:21,666
we will also invade the Earth.

48
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,791
[HARUHI]
Cut!

49
00:02:22,875 --> 00:02:25,083
I-I won't let you
get away with that!

50
00:02:25,166 --> 00:02:27,208
I will risk my own life
to stop you!

51
00:02:27,291 --> 00:02:28,250
[HARUHI]
Cut!

52
00:02:29,541 --> 00:02:31,666
See? You're startin'
to get the hang of it!

53
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:32,875
Good job!

54
00:02:32,958 --> 00:02:34,375
Okay, c'mere a sec.

55
00:02:34,458 --> 00:02:36,500
I gotta talk to you
about the next shot.

56
00:02:36,583 --> 00:02:38,333
[MIKURU]
Okay...

57
00:02:39,833 --> 00:02:41,666
[KYON]
I hope we get out of here soon,

58
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:45,250
before anybody in the
neighborhood notices we're here.

59
00:02:45,333 --> 00:02:47,375
So that's your
video camera, huh?

60
00:02:47,458 --> 00:02:51,250
[laughs] I betcha got a lotta
goofy shots of Mikuru on there.

61
00:02:51,333 --> 00:02:54,291
[laughing]

62
00:02:54,375 --> 00:02:56,000
[KYON]
I don't see what's so funny.

63
00:02:56,083 --> 00:02:58,250
There's a lot of
damaging stuff in there.

64
00:02:58,333 --> 00:03:01,083
What if Miss Asahina stops
coming to school because of it?

65
00:03:01,166 --> 00:03:02,333
[HARUHI]
We're back!

66
00:03:02,416 --> 00:03:04,708
And we're gonna be
kickin' things up a notch!

67
00:03:04,791 --> 00:03:05,541
Check it out!

68
00:03:05,625 --> 00:03:06,875
Cool, huh?

69
00:03:08,166 --> 00:03:09,416
[KYON]
Oh god, no!

70
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:11,708
It's gonna be a repeat of
what happened yesterday!

71
00:03:11,791 --> 00:03:13,208
This is bad!

72
00:03:13,291 --> 00:03:14,625
Go ahead, Mikuru.

73
00:03:14,708 --> 00:03:17,625
I don't care what comes
outta that miracle Mikuru IR.

74
00:03:17,708 --> 00:03:19,833
Whatever it is, make sure
it's destructive!

75
00:03:19,916 --> 00:03:21,083
[yelps]

76
00:03:21,166 --> 00:03:22,166
[MIKURU screams]

77
00:03:24,875 --> 00:03:26,083
[HARUHI]
Oh, come on, Yuki!

78
00:03:26,166 --> 00:03:27,791
You're supposed to be
an evil witch!

79
00:03:27,875 --> 00:03:30,708
Stop whipping out
the wrestling moves!

80
00:03:30,791 --> 00:03:32,750
Well, I guess this works, too.

81
00:03:32,833 --> 00:03:34,708
Whatever gets more viewers.

82
00:03:34,791 --> 00:03:36,666
Hey, Kyon!
Why aren't you rolling?

83
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:39,541
This is Yuki's concept!
Don't waste it!

84
00:03:39,625 --> 00:03:41,625
[KYON]
It's not a concept.

85
00:03:41,708 --> 00:03:43,125
This is racy stuff...

86
00:03:43,208 --> 00:03:44,583
I shouldn't be
shooting this, but...

87
00:03:44,666 --> 00:03:46,416
Put the target in
the center and hit record.

88
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:47,750
No, I mustn't, I mustn't.

89
00:03:47,833 --> 00:03:48,750
[crash]

90
00:03:48,833 --> 00:03:49,958
[GROUP]
Huh?

91
00:03:55,625 --> 00:03:58,250
You better leave
this planet at once!

92
00:03:58,333 --> 00:04:01,541
[HARUHI] Oh, geez! I can't
believe we lost another contact!

93
00:04:01,625 --> 00:04:02,875
My mistake.

94
00:04:02,958 --> 00:04:05,625
I disabled the laser function
she had access to.

95
00:04:05,708 --> 00:04:10,500
However, a high-frequency
molecular cutter was activated.

96
00:04:10,583 --> 00:04:11,625
[BOTH gasp]

97
00:04:13,458 --> 00:04:16,291
That looks like damage
from a monofilament attack.

98
00:04:16,375 --> 00:04:17,250
Oh, no!

99
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:19,541
I'm really sorry about that.

100
00:04:19,625 --> 00:04:23,000
But, um... what did you
inject me with this time?

101
00:04:25,041 --> 00:04:28,041
I altered the phase of
your dimensional cycles,

102
00:04:28,125 --> 00:04:30,958
and generated a force
field around your body,

103
00:04:31,041 --> 00:04:33,625
which alters
gravitational waves.

104
00:04:33,708 --> 00:04:35,166
I understand.

105
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:37,625
For the time being, it looks
like it's been taken care of.

106
00:04:37,708 --> 00:04:38,916
[KYON]
Yep, still don't get it.

107
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,750
As for what happened
to the fence,

108
00:04:40,833 --> 00:04:43,958
the others seem to think
it was old and falling apart.

109
00:04:44,041 --> 00:04:47,166
And thankfully, it was the only
thing that got damaged.

110
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,833
Yeah, but what are we gonna do?

111
00:04:48,916 --> 00:04:50,625
I mean, if we keep
shooting this thing,

112
00:04:50,708 --> 00:04:52,958
I'm scared that something
really bad's gonna happen.

113
00:04:53,041 --> 00:04:56,083
Regardless, we can't interfere
with the completion of the film.

114
00:04:56,166 --> 00:04:58,083
Can you imagine what
Miss Suzumiya would do

115
00:04:58,166 --> 00:05:00,583
if we tried to force her
to stop shooting it?

116
00:05:00,666 --> 00:05:02,333
[KYON sighs]

117
00:05:02,416 --> 00:05:03,541
I don't care.

118
00:05:03,625 --> 00:05:05,833
I guarantee,
she wouldn't be happy at all.

119
00:05:05,916 --> 00:05:10,208
A closed space would be
torn apart by the Shinjin.

120
00:05:10,291 --> 00:05:11,291
You have to understand,

121
00:05:11,375 --> 00:05:13,083
Miss Suzumiya's
having so much fun,

122
00:05:13,166 --> 00:05:14,833
she just can't help herself.

123
00:05:14,916 --> 00:05:18,083
And in a way, this is a
chance for her to play god.

124
00:05:18,166 --> 00:05:19,916
The process of putting
the movie together

125
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,208
is Miss Suzumiya's way
of creating a world

126
00:05:22,291 --> 00:05:24,416
that functions
according to her will.

127
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:26,416
[KYON]
Selfish as ever, I see.

128
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,791
Of course, Miss Suzumiya doesn't

129
00:05:27,875 --> 00:05:29,750
realize any of this
is happening.

130
00:05:29,833 --> 00:05:31,666
She thinks she's creating
a fictional world

131
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,333
for the story of her movie.

132
00:05:34,416 --> 00:05:37,375
However, I believe
that subconsciously,

133
00:05:37,458 --> 00:05:39,833
she's so passionate about it,
she's actually starting

134
00:05:39,916 --> 00:05:42,083
to change the reality
of this world.

135
00:05:42,166 --> 00:05:43,791
[KYON]
Fiction, he says.

136
00:05:43,875 --> 00:05:47,250
Either way you slice it,
we get a bad ending.

137
00:05:47,333 --> 00:05:48,666
If we have to choose between

138
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:51,666
stopping the shoot or
seeing it through to the end,

139
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:54,666
I would strongly recommend
we finish it.

140
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:58,375
Even if Miss Asahina turns
into some kind of super woman?

141
00:05:58,458 --> 00:06:00,250
Compared to having
the Shinjin appear,

142
00:06:00,333 --> 00:06:02,125
it's a small price to pay.

143
00:06:02,208 --> 00:06:03,291
Think about it.

144
00:06:03,375 --> 00:06:04,583
Wouldn't it be easier
to deal with

145
00:06:04,666 --> 00:06:07,541
abnormal phenomena
one at a time, as opposed to

146
00:06:07,625 --> 00:06:11,208
having the world rebuilt from
scratch right under your feet?

147
00:06:11,291 --> 00:06:12,791
[KYON s

148
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:15,750
If you ask me, it's all pretty
much the same thing, isn't it?

149
00:06:15,833 --> 00:06:17,625
Here's another option
for us to consider:

150
00:06:17,708 --> 00:06:19,041
We could knock Haruhi out cold

151
00:06:19,125 --> 00:06:21,208
and wake her up
after the festival's over.

152
00:06:21,291 --> 00:06:23,666
That's a frightening
thought to consider.

153
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:27,166
But if you're prepared to take
responsibility for the outcome,

154
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:28,791
I wouldn't get in your way.

155
00:06:28,875 --> 00:06:30,875
[grunts]

156
00:06:30,958 --> 00:06:32,458
[growls]

157
00:06:32,541 --> 00:06:35,416
I don't think my shoulders can
handle the weight of the world.

158
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,833
[MIKURU]
Um...

159
00:06:36,916 --> 00:06:39,708
I don't want you
to worry about me.

160
00:06:39,791 --> 00:06:42,500
I'll be okay and find a way
to get through this.

161
00:06:42,583 --> 00:06:44,041
[gasps]

162
00:06:44,125 --> 00:06:47,083
[KYON]
I am in awe of her selflessness!

163
00:06:47,166 --> 00:06:49,333
[HARUHI] These are the
characters you guys play.

164
00:06:49,416 --> 00:06:50,333
Here's the deal,

165
00:06:50,416 --> 00:06:51,666
since Mikuru's the hero,

166
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,916
she doesn't believe
in hurting innocent people.

167
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,416
Yuki takes advantage of this

168
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:58,125
and uses her magic to
get you guys to attack her.

169
00:06:58,208 --> 00:06:59,750
Since Mikuru wouldn't
hurt you guys,

170
00:06:59,833 --> 00:07:00,791
she gets beaten up!

171
00:07:00,875 --> 00:07:02,458
[GROUP gasps]

172
00:07:02,541 --> 00:07:04,375
Mikuru's gonna get beaten up!

173
00:07:04,458 --> 00:07:05,916
Here's what you do!

174
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,500
The three of you are gonna throw
Mikuru right into the lake!

175
00:07:08,583 --> 00:07:10,125
[BOTH gasp]

176
00:07:10,208 --> 00:07:12,708
Wait a second,
you wanna throw her in there?

177
00:07:12,791 --> 00:07:15,291
The water might be warm
but it's cold out!

178
00:07:15,375 --> 00:07:17,250
Besides, that water's
pretty filthy!

179
00:07:17,333 --> 00:07:21,458
B-But Miss Suzumiya,
couldn't we do this at a pool?

180
00:07:21,541 --> 00:07:23,916
No one said this shoot
was gonna be easy.

181
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,708
So suck it up already!

182
00:07:25,791 --> 00:07:27,708
You have to make
these kinds of sacrifices,

183
00:07:27,791 --> 00:07:31,375
especially if they're gonna help
us get the realism we're after!

184
00:07:31,458 --> 00:07:33,666
You can't let something
like this stand in your way!

185
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:35,083
You have to overcome it!

186
00:07:35,166 --> 00:07:37,583
This is a big step up
for you as an actress!

187
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:38,875
See what I'm saying?

188
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:40,375
Good! Get ready!

189
00:07:40,458 --> 00:07:41,541
Hang on!

190
00:07:43,208 --> 00:07:44,625
[KOIZUMI]
Mm-mm.

191
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:55,708
I-I'll... Okay! I'll do it!

192
00:07:55,791 --> 00:07:56,958
Thatta girl!

193
00:07:57,041 --> 00:07:58,208
Yes!

194
00:07:58,291 --> 00:08:00,250
That's why I picked you
to be a brigade member!

195
00:08:00,333 --> 00:08:02,375
[MIKURU whimpers]

196
00:08:02,458 --> 00:08:04,041
[KYON]
Miss Asahina...

197
00:08:04,125 --> 00:08:05,500
One, two, three!

198
00:08:05,583 --> 00:08:07,125
[MIKURU screams]

199
00:08:10,291 --> 00:08:11,750
[KYON]
Heaven protect her.

200
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:14,666
[KOIZUMI] What's happening?
Just grab my hand. It's okay.

201
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:16,500
[coughs]

202
00:08:19,166 --> 00:08:20,458
[KYON]
Good grief!

203
00:08:20,541 --> 00:08:23,208
We've got enough crap here
to open up a pawn shop,

204
00:08:23,291 --> 00:08:24,750
but we don't
have a towel for her?

205
00:08:24,833 --> 00:08:26,416
What's up with that?

206
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:27,708
[HARUHI]
Hm...

207
00:08:27,791 --> 00:08:29,375
This could work for the
scene where they meet.

208
00:08:29,458 --> 00:08:32,458
You can feel the awkwardness
between Itsuki and Mikuru.

209
00:08:32,541 --> 00:08:33,958
[KYON]
Really?

210
00:08:34,041 --> 00:08:36,375
Looked like Koizumi was just
acting like he always does.

211
00:08:37,833 --> 00:08:39,625
We're moving on
to the next setup!

212
00:08:39,708 --> 00:08:41,916
It's the scene right
after Itsuki saves Mikuru,

213
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,500
where he picks her up and
carries her back to his house.

214
00:08:44,583 --> 00:08:45,583
[gasps]

215
00:08:45,666 --> 00:08:46,666
Hang on!

216
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,666
That makes absolutely
no sense at all!

217
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:51,291
What happened to Nagato,
Taniguchi, and the others?!

218
00:08:51,375 --> 00:08:52,833
The audience is
gonna get totally lost

219
00:08:52,916 --> 00:08:54,750
if they just disappear
from the story!

220
00:08:54,833 --> 00:08:56,125
Oh, be quiet!

221
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:58,125
The audience is gonna be
so wrapped up in the story,

222
00:08:58,208 --> 00:08:59,458
they'll be fine with it!

223
00:08:59,541 --> 00:09:00,875
[KYON]
No they won't!

224
00:09:00,958 --> 00:09:03,625
You just wanna see Miss Asahina
get tossed in the lake!

225
00:09:03,708 --> 00:09:05,208
My house isn't
too far from here,

226
00:09:05,291 --> 00:09:07,375
and Mikuru looks
like she's freezing.

227
00:09:07,458 --> 00:09:09,041
Is it cool if
she changes clothes?

228
00:09:09,125 --> 00:09:12,041
'Cause she might end up
catching a cold!

229
00:09:12,125 --> 00:09:13,375
That's a great idea!

230
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:15,625
Can we use your house
for our next location?

231
00:09:15,708 --> 00:09:17,125
It's the perfect place
to shoot the scene

232
00:09:17,208 --> 00:09:19,208
where they get all
friendly with each other!

233
00:09:19,291 --> 00:09:21,750
Yep! Go ahead,
knock yourself out!

234
00:09:21,833 --> 00:09:23,416
Uh, what do you want us to do?

235
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:25,291
You can go home.
I'm done with you.

236
00:09:25,375 --> 00:09:26,625
[BOTH]
Huh?!

237
00:09:26,708 --> 00:09:29,000
[KYON] Congratulations,
you guys have been sacked.

238
00:09:29,083 --> 00:09:31,083
It looks like you're about
as important to Haruhi

239
00:09:31,166 --> 00:09:33,375
as a bunch of spent BBs.

240
00:09:33,458 --> 00:09:36,958
Which isn't such a bad thing,
if you wanna know the truth.

241
00:09:37,041 --> 00:09:38,791
[TSURUYA]
Ta-da! Here it is!

242
00:09:38,875 --> 00:09:41,041
[KYON]
Ginormous!

243
00:09:41,125 --> 00:09:43,125
What sorts of evil things
do I have to do

244
00:09:43,208 --> 00:09:44,916
to live in a place like this?

245
00:09:46,083 --> 00:09:48,000
So anyway, this is my room!

246
00:09:48,083 --> 00:09:50,958
You guys can wait here till
Mikuru's done with her bath.

247
00:09:51,041 --> 00:09:52,666
[KYON] Whoa, this place
makes my bedroom

248
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:54,291
look like a cat condo.

249
00:09:54,375 --> 00:09:55,625
[HARUHI]
Great room!

250
00:09:55,708 --> 00:09:57,791
This is a perfect location!

251
00:09:57,875 --> 00:09:59,000
Oh, yeah!

252
00:09:59,083 --> 00:10:01,625
Hey, Tsuru, I wanted
to ask you something.

253
00:10:01,708 --> 00:10:03,791
When you get the...
[whispering continues]

254
00:10:03,875 --> 00:10:07,833
[laughs]

255
00:10:07,916 --> 00:10:08,875
[KYON]
Huh?

256
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:11,250
[TSURUYA]
Sorry to keep you waiting!

257
00:10:11,333 --> 00:10:12,083
Here you go.

258
00:10:12,166 --> 00:10:13,500
Thank you!

259
00:10:13,583 --> 00:10:14,708
Thanks for waiting.

260
00:10:14,791 --> 00:10:16,250
Sorry I took so long.

261
00:10:16,333 --> 00:10:17,541
[TSURUYA]
Here you go!

262
00:10:17,625 --> 00:10:18,791
[KYON gasps]

263
00:10:18,875 --> 00:10:20,500
[KYON] Am I being
tested here or something?!

264
00:10:20,583 --> 00:10:23,750
Miss Asahina, that outfit
is absolutely criminal!

265
00:10:23,833 --> 00:10:25,708
Here you go! Drink up!

266
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,208
[KYON]
Thanks.

267
00:10:29,291 --> 00:10:30,458
Thank you.

268
00:10:32,375 --> 00:10:33,375
[KYON]
Watching her take a sip

269
00:10:33,458 --> 00:10:35,500
