to my libido!

270
00:10:35,583 --> 00:10:37,333
Okay, let's knock this one out!

271
00:10:37,416 --> 00:10:39,708
[KYON] And with that,
we started shooting.

272
00:10:39,791 --> 00:10:41,333
In the shot, Koizumi carried the

273
00:10:41,416 --> 00:10:44,708
pretending-to-be-unconscious
Miss Asahina into the room.

274
00:10:44,791 --> 00:10:46,583
For some unknown
and convenient reason,

275
00:10:46,666 --> 00:10:49,333
there was a futon
spread out on the floor.

276
00:10:49,416 --> 00:10:51,416
Go, Mikuru, start waking up.

277
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,625
[whimpers]

278
00:10:52,708 --> 00:10:54,375
[KOIZUMI]
Are you awake now?

279
00:10:56,125 --> 00:10:57,041
Yes...

280
00:10:57,125 --> 00:10:59,958
But, um...
I don't know where I am.

281
00:11:00,041 --> 00:11:01,708
[KOIZUMI]
You're in my room now.

282
00:11:01,791 --> 00:11:03,916
Thank you for taking care of me.

283
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,708
[KYON]
She seems a little too sexy.

284
00:11:05,791 --> 00:11:06,875
Is that acting?

285
00:11:06,958 --> 00:11:08,541
[HARUHI] Bring your faces
closer together.

286
00:11:08,625 --> 00:11:09,416
Yeah!

287
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:11,166
Now, Mikuru, close your eyes.

288
00:11:11,250 --> 00:11:13,333
Koizumi, put your
arm around her!

289
00:11:14,541 --> 00:11:17,208
All right, now push
her down and kiss her!

290
00:11:17,291 --> 00:11:18,250
[grunts]

291
00:11:23,250 --> 00:11:24,208
[growls]

292
00:11:26,208 --> 00:11:27,250
Hold it!

293
00:11:28,375 --> 00:11:29,541
This is going too far!

294
00:11:29,625 --> 00:11:31,375
Why is this scene
happening anyway?!

295
00:11:31,458 --> 00:11:32,833
What is this?!

296
00:11:32,916 --> 00:11:34,750
It's a love scene, of course.

297
00:11:34,833 --> 00:11:37,625
We have to have one to
pat out the picture's runtime.

298
00:11:37,708 --> 00:11:39,000
You're crazy!

299
00:11:39,083 --> 00:11:41,416
Are we shooting a movie
for late-night TV or what?!

300
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:44,000
And why are you suddenly
getting into it, Koizumi?!

301
00:11:44,083 --> 00:11:46,041
If this thing ever screens
at the school festival,

302
00:11:46,125 --> 00:11:48,083
I guarantee you're gonna
get a ton of hate mail

303
00:11:48,166 --> 00:11:50,250
crammed in your shoe
locker the next day!

304
00:11:50,333 --> 00:11:51,500
I'll even write some myself!

305
00:11:51,583 --> 00:11:52,958
[TSURUYA laughs]

306
00:11:53,041 --> 00:11:55,125
Mikuru, you're so weird!

307
00:11:55,208 --> 00:11:56,750
[KYON]
Normally, I'd disagree,

308
00:11:56,833 --> 00:11:59,083
but she is acting
a little strange.

309
00:11:59,166 --> 00:12:02,041
Her eyes are all glazed over,
and her cheeks are flushed.

310
00:12:02,125 --> 00:12:04,916
She looks like she'd let
Koizumi do whatever he wants!

311
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,041
This isn't funny anymore!

312
00:12:07,125 --> 00:12:11,458
Hey... Koizumi, I feel hot...
and my head's all heavy...

313
00:12:11,541 --> 00:12:14,583
[KYON] Geez, it's like somebody
drugged her or something.

314
00:12:14,666 --> 00:12:15,625
[gasps]

315
00:12:18,583 --> 00:12:22,125
Sorry, I sorta spiked her juice
with a little bit of sake.

316
00:12:22,208 --> 00:12:24,958
