loosen up and act better.

317
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:29,416
[HARUHI]
Hmph.

318
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:31,541
It's not right to get
people loaded like that!

319
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:34,833
Just look at her, she's sexier
now than ever before!

320
00:12:34,916 --> 00:12:36,958
Don't listen to him,
kiss her! Go ahead!

321
00:12:37,041 --> 00:12:38,583
Kiss her right on the mouth!

322
00:12:38,666 --> 00:12:39,541
[growls]

323
00:12:39,625 --> 00:12:41,208
Don't do it, Koizumi.

324
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:46,916
Madam Director...

325
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,625
I hate to say it, but I'm
feeling a little overwhelmed.

326
00:12:49,708 --> 00:12:51,625
Besides, it looks like
Miss Asahina's

327
00:12:51,708 --> 00:12:53,250
reached her limit, too.

328
00:12:53,333 --> 00:12:56,708
Nah... I feel fine...
Let's keep shouting...

329
00:12:56,791 --> 00:12:59,708
Aw, geez! This won't do...

330
00:12:59,791 --> 00:13:00,750
[MIKURU]
Huh?

331
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:04,916
Man, I can't believe
you'd get so plastered

332
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,875
from just a little sake.

333
00:13:06,958 --> 00:13:08,666
[KYON] I can't believe
you made her drink it!

334
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:11,083
Come on, snap out of it!

335
00:13:11,166 --> 00:13:12,208
[yelps]

336
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,875
You call that a reaction?

337
00:13:15,958 --> 00:13:17,916
Whenever I tap you on
the head with this thing,

338
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,583
you have to straighten
out your back.

339
00:13:19,666 --> 00:13:20,958
That's the rule!

340
00:13:21,791 --> 00:13:24,416
Let's try it again, okay?
Now focus!

341
00:13:25,541 --> 00:13:26,500
[yelps]

342
00:13:33,916 --> 00:13:34,875
[yelps]

343
00:13:36,875 --> 00:13:38,125
[KYON]
Cut it out!

344
00:13:38,208 --> 00:13:39,791
How is that supposed to help?!

345
00:13:39,875 --> 00:13:42,041
And how is any of this
gonna fit in the movie?!

346
00:13:42,125 --> 00:13:43,875
Huh?! What's your problem?

347
00:13:43,958 --> 00:13:45,958
I don't have to tell you
how I'm gonna use this,

348
00:13:46,041 --> 00:13:48,041
